Subject: Collection for infrastructure Cloud and DBs
Description: We're looking to create Collections for cloud-based apps and on-prem databases and wanted to know what is possible out-of-the-box and what is needed to do these type of scans.
What_We_Know__c:
Customer is asking for out of the box solutions and what their requirements are. Provided links to existing documentation.

https://helpcenter.netwrix.com/bundle/EnterpriseAuditor_11.6/page/Content/EnterpriseAuditor/Solutions/Overview.htm
https://helpcenter.netwrix.com/bundle/EnterpriseAuditor_11.6/page/Content/EnterpriseAuditor/Requirements/Overview.htm
Solution_Comment__c:
Symptom
Customer is looking for details on what types of collections for cloud based applications NEA has out of the box.


Resolution
Provided documentation and referred to sales team as the licensing needed to do the collections requested is not available to this customer at this time.
